cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

The paper deals with the generation of textures and stylized images using deep neural networks. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The authors also mention the use of complex and expressive loss functions, which suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also includes examples of generating textures for graphics applications, which could fall under computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
